'''Antropologie''' ye donni yé mi bɛ tali kɛ [[adamadéya]] kan. A bɛ adamadé kalan a fan bɛ ladjɛléfɛ. Djɛkulubola, sigiyorobola, kɛtiokoyabola, kokètiokoyaw ani takabolo. Ale kalanbolo sinsinibɛ mokow kɛtiokoyala jɛkulukono, jɛkulu minu tɛ jekulu baw ye. [[Etnologie]] oye ka siyaw kalani ye, anthropologie oye ka adamadé yɛrɛde kalan, kalancokobɛladjɛla.

Takabolo caman bɛ antropologila, minu nafakabo kosɛbɛ oluye [[sociologie|sociologikalanso]] mi bɛ fransikawfɛ ye ([[Emile Durkheim]], [[Marcel Mauss]], [[Claude Levi-Strauss]]), anthropologie mibɛ jɛkukuwkan Anglew fɛ ye ([[James George Frazer|J.G. Frazer]]), [[Bronislaw Malinoski]], [[Alfred Reginal Radcliffe-Brown|A.R. Radcliffe-Brown]], [[Edward Evan Evans-Pritchard|E.E. Evans-Pritchard]], a ni anthropologie mibɛ kokɛtiokoyawkan Amerikawfɛ ye ([[Lewis Henry Morgan|L.H. Morgan]], [[Franz Boas]], [[Marvin Harris]], [[Clifford Geertz]]).

